{"tid":1750995,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"請放心吸收二噁英 - 高慧然","createTime":"2019-11-24T15:07:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T16:47:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0634db9c5c8cde71e729d2d859f2bf22c6695d9e","tid":1750995,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:07:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20191123/20811638/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191123%2F20811638%2F&d=8H50EXT8eKO%2B303r5eJ0KJa0YVntLK4LebkCjpCDSOM%3D&h=ea8f0871\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191123%2F20811638%2F&h=4ecfa68a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20191123/20811638/</a><br />\n<br />\n請放心吸收二噁英 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191123/large/1574416402_48d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191123%2Flarge%2F1574416402_48d5.jpg&h=ae88ac1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n反逃犯修訂條例引發的示威活動持續至今，香港人已堅持了半年之久，而警方濫發的催淚彈數目則累積近一萬個，遍及港九新界，幾乎無一地方倖免。催淚煙殘留空氣及物件表面，對人體健康及生態環境造成多大的破壞？已引起巿民憂慮。<br />\n<br />\n有化學工程師自發在金鐘、上環、西營盤、九龍灣、深水埗、荃灣等收集兩百多個物件表面的塵埃樣本作分析，發現八月十八日在上環及西營盤收集到的樣本，仍測出CS化學物，而追溯該區上一次施放催淚彈，則是七月二十八日，即二十一天前。研究結果與政府強調催淚煙殘留時間不長的說法大有出入。<br />\n<br />\n中國製催淚彈最大的問題是極高溫，而高溫最終會導致CS釋放出二噁英。二噁英一旦進入人體，永遠無法排走，對環境及人體的禍害不止一代人。化學專家及醫學界表現出極大關注，醫學界呼籲有生育計劃的香港人重新規劃人生大計，在兩年內避免懷孕。<br />\n<br />\n可是，政府不是公佈催淚彈成份以釋公眾憂慮，食物及衛生局局長陳肇始更以會妨礙警方部署為由，拒絕公開成份。任由警方繼續在全港各區以化學武器無差別慢性殺人。政府更拍了一段宣傳片放上網絡，說明催淚彈很安全，此舉無異於鼓勵民眾放心吸收二噁英。某一日，若被證實政府撒了彌天大謊，不止一代人的悲劇已無法逆轉，整個問責團隊百死不能贖其罪。 <br />\n<br />\n高慧然<br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk"},{"pid":"73ceea1d9afca677e8d130676c05f8e01de41a94","tid":1750995,"uid":204527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:22:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c04d8ae02db8d9afa59fee3b804c0ee44d5c4a97","tid":1750995,"uid":131121,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:40:03.000Z","msg":"條八婆食錯藥，定係佢屋企射tg"},{"pid":"6d5a0e571dbb7e520def726675948b2072602cec","tid":1750995,"uid":15592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c04d8ae02db8d9afa59fee3b804c0ee44d5c4a97","tid":1750995,"uid":131121,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:40:03.000Z","msg":"條八婆食錯藥，定係佢屋企射tg"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:45:03.000Z","msg":"你講高慧然？一直都深黃喎"},{"pid":"150ae27a6d729bf283e13cd3615fa26a773b0456","tid":1750995,"uid":248351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c04d8ae02db8d9afa59fee3b804c0ee44d5c4a97","tid":1750995,"uid":131121,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:40:03.000Z","msg":"條八婆食錯藥，定係佢屋企射tg"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:46:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d646b713f1d6bc359aa521c699e5598c6125e8ec","tid":1750995,"uid":153239,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6d5a0e571dbb7e520def726675948b2072602cec","tid":1750995,"uid":15592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c04d8ae02db8d9afa59fee3b804c0ee44d5c4a97","tid":1750995,"uid":131121,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:40:03.000Z","msg":"條八婆食錯藥，定係佢屋企射tg"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:45:03.000Z","msg":"你講高慧然？一直都深黃喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:46:38.000Z","msg":"佢係咪應錯左屈小姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65efb927022f29ac1fcafce2db439b8b0e56bd29","tid":1750995,"uid":278184,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c04d8ae02db8d9